{
    "text": "The Italian Dolomites may not have the height and grandeur of the snow-covered French peaks or cute villages and steep-sided valleys of the Swiss Alps. But what sets the Dolomites apart are the dramatic limestone peaks. Crags that soar out of rolling green meadows. A landscape different from other alpine areas \u2013 where the change from rural idyll to inhospitable mountain is swift and stunning. Who would you take a hike here with? \u2063 \u2063 \ud83d\udccc The Dolomites, Italy \ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf9\u2063 \u2063 \u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\u2063\ud83d\udcf8 Thank you @ilhan1077 @tomarcherphoto @mattworldph @angelaliggs @mikesugianto @everchanginghorizon @jess.wandering @d_laguna90 and @rikscan for your great photos!\u2063 \u2063 \u2705 If you want to be featured too, don't forget to follow @hikingtheglobe and tag # hikingtheglobe in your photos. Cheers!\u2063",
